## Core Configuration
```yaml
name: "&a&l%voidchest% VoidChest Inventory"
size: 54
animation:
  enabled: true
```
- **Dynamic Title**: Uses `%voidchest%` placeholder for chest name
- **Standard Size**: 6-row inventory (54 slots)
- **Animations**: Global wave animation with color gradients

