## Dynamic Placeholders

| Placeholder   | Description     | Example Output      |
|---------------|-----------------|---------------------|
| `%voidchest%` | Chest name/tier | "Premium VoidChest" |
| `%status_*%`  | Feature state   | "Enabled"           |
| `%!status_*%` | Opposite state  | "Disable"           |
| `%charge%`    | Remaining time  | "02:30:00"          |
| `%money%`     | Earnings        | "12,450.00"         |

## Animation System
```yaml
animation: "wave"
colors:
  - "#F3F8FA"
  - "#1E4356"
```
- **Wave Effect**: Smooth color transition
- **5-Color Gradients**: Predefined palettes
- **Global Toggle**: Enabled/disabled in root config

